<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title><%= @event.title %> on <%= @event.date.format("dddd, MMMM DD YYYY") %></title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../artlist.css">
<body class="avenir">
  <article>
    <header>
      <h1><b><%= @event.title %></b></h1>
      <h2><%= @event.artist %></h2>
      <h2><a><%= @event.date.format("dddd") %> <%= @event.date.format("MMMM DD YYYY") %></a></h2>
      <h2>8pm until Midnight</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="location">
      <h2><b><%= @event.location.name %></b></h2>
      <h2><a href=""><%= @event.location.address %>, <%= @event.location.city %></a></h2>
    </div>
    <div>
      <%- @event.enHTML %>
    </div>
    <div>
      <a href=""><%= @event.website %></a>
    </div>
  </article>

<footer>

<p>
  <b><a href="">Artlist</a></b> is a place to discover arts events in the Ottawa-Gatineau region. <a href="">Artlist</a> is curated by <a href="">Artengine</a>.
</p>
<p>
To add an event to <a href="">Artlist</a> please send a short summary or a photograph of a the event poster to <a href="mailto:artlist@artengine.ca">artlist@artengine.ca</a>.
If you are sending your first posting please <a href="">read our event guidelines</a> before sending your email.
</p>

</footer>
</body>
